OL,3,CSellafield fined more than #330,000
OL,4,Cfor cybersecurity failings
OL,6,FSellafield Ltd has been fined more
OL,7,Fthan #330,000 for failings in
OL,8,Fcybersecurity.
OL,10,FThe firm, which operates the nuclear
OL,11,Fsite in west Cumbria, was charged
OL,12,Fafter an investigation by the Office
OL,13,Ffor Nuclear Regulation (ONR) found it
OL,14,Ffailed to meet standards for
OL,15,Fprotecting sensitive nuclear
OL,16,Finformation.
