OL,3,CSellafield fined more than #330,000
OL,4,Cfor cybersecurity failings
OL,6,FThe ONR did not find that any
OL,7,Fvulnerabilities had been exploited as
OL,8,Fa result of the failings, but said its
OL,9,Fsystems were vulnerable to
OL,10,Funauthorised access and loss of data.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court, Chief Magistrate
OL,14,FPaul Goldspring fined the company
OL,15,F#332,500 and ordered it to pay
OL,16,Fprosecution costs of #53,253.
OL,18,FThe company had pleaded guilty at an
OL,19,Fearlier hearing to three counts of
OL,20,Ffailing to comply with its approved
OL,21,Fsecurity plan.
