OL,3,CSellafield fined more than #330,000
OL,4,Cfor cybersecurity failings
OL,6,FPaul Fyfe, the ONR's senior director
OL,7,Fof regulation, said: "It has been
OL,8,Faccepted the company's ability to
OL,9,Fcomply with certain obligations under
OL,10,Fthe Nuclear Industries Security
OL,11,FRegulations 2003 during a period of
OL,12,Ffour years was poor.
OL,14,F"Failings were known about for a
OL,15,Fconsiderable length of time but
OL,16,Fdespite our interventions and
OL,17,Fguidance, Sellafield failed to respond
OL,18,Feffectively, which left it vulnerable
OL,19,Fto security breaches and its systems
OL,20,Fbeing compromised.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
