OL,3,CSellafield fined more than #330,000
OL,4,Cfor cybersecurity failings
OL,6,F"Nevertheless, with new leadership and
OL,7,Fadditional resources in place at
OL,8,FSellafield Ltd, we have seen positive
OL,9,Fimprovements during the last year, and
OL,10,Fevidence the senior leadership is now
OL,11,Fgiving cybersecurity the level of
OL,12,Fattention and focus it requires."
OL,14,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said: "We
OL,15,Ftake the safety of our nationally
OL,16,Fsignificant infrastructure very
OL,17,Fseriously and I welcome the fact we
OL,18,Fhave a robust regulator holding our
OL,19,Fnuclear industry to account.
